data.description: Light and bright end unit in sought after Bartram Springs featuring one of the few open concept floor plans.  New, wood look, floor tile downstairs with upstairs carpet recently replaced.  Upstairs has a flex space perfect for office or hobby area.  'A' rated school inside the neighborhood and first class amenities, including two pools, fitness center, clubhouse, playgrounds & soccer fields.  Close to shopping, restaurants & easy access to I95.  FHA 3.125% assumable loan.  Buyer must qualify for the assumption and use a release of liability to sellers
